
'''= "DAISEE is a action-research program for people who consider [[Energy as a Common]](s)".'''

URL = https://daisee.org/

"Our goal: Build the conditions for the *shared governance* of energy at the local and regional scale by ALL grid stakeholders."


=Status=

"In 2018, we've joined the Energy Commons movement, initiated by Energy Collective (Danemark) with the ambition to build an european federation acting for energy transition(s) through commons.

In 2019, with the support of Oxamyne, we're (1) developing a 'research cooperative' to empower the energy transition infrastructure of Prats-de-Mollo (2) converging toward a FabMob like dynamics on "energy"."


